.

1. *Sila* je jedna od najvećih vrlina. (Strength is one of the greatest virtues.)
2. Preterivana *sila* je najčešći razlog nasilja. (Excessive force is the most common cause of violence.)
3. Ona je svojom *silom* uspela da preokrene situaciju. (She was able to turn the situation around with her strength.)
4. Oni su se borili sa *silom* protiv nečega što ne mogu da promene. (They were fighting against something they couldn't change with force.)
5. *Silu* treba koristiti samo u ekstremnim situacijama. (Force should only be used in extreme situations.)